OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fwarm and sunny evening then a dry
OL,7,Fnight with some clear spells, and a
OL,8,Flittle cloud at times. Winds will
OL,9,Fremain light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FAnother bright day with some
OL,12,Fsunshine at times and becoming hot
OL,13,Faway from sea breezes, especially in
OL,14,Fthe southwest. Overnight there is a
OL,15,Fchance of some heavy showers in east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
