OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,6,Fcooler, cloudier Saturday in east but
OL,7,Fsunny in the west. Cloudy start Sunday
OL,8,Fthen brightening up with sunny
OL,9,Fintervals. Monday dry and sunny. Very
OL,10,Fwarm in west, cooler east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
